                      current map.
   [bullet-lnb.gif]   Maps are updated within 5 minutes of an earthquake
                      and once an hour.
   [bullet-lnb.gif]   Magnitude = ? for new earthquakes until a magnitude
                      is determined (4-5 minutes).
   [bullet-lnb.gif]   Brown lines are known hazardous faults and fault
                      zones.

